description:
Bob Ross fans! It’s ‘time’ for some happy trees, and we’ve got just what you need: https://pxlfy.me/BobRossWatchMightyMojoToys
Narrow, winding, rocky – this little Bob Ross style creek moves closer and closer, flowing aimlessly through a happy little meadow forest. 

Season 6 of The Joy of Painting with Bob Ross features the following wonderful painting instructions: Blue River, Nature's Edge, Morning Mist, Whispering Stream, Secluded Forest, Snow Trail, Arctic Beauty, Horizons West, High Chateau, Country Life, Western Expanse, Marshlands, and Blaze of Color.

Subscribe to the official Bob Ross YouTube channel - http://bit.ly/BobRossSubscribe

Season 6 Playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLAEQD0ULngi5UR35RJsvL0Xvlm3oeY4Ma
title: Bob Ross - Whispering Stream (Season 6 Episode 4)
